|DA|^2 = |DB|^2 + |AB|^2 - 2|AB||DB|\cos(x)
|DC|^2 = |DB|^2 + |BC|^2 - 2|BC||DB|\cos(y)
x + y = \pi
|DA| = r_A + |DB|
|DC| = r_C + |DB|
|AB| = |BC|
(r_A + |DB|)^2 = |DB|^2 + |AB|^2 - 2|AB||DB|\cos(x)
(r_C + |DB|)^2 = |DB|^2 + |AB|^2 - 2|AB||DB|\cos(\pi - x)
\cos(\pi - x) = \cos(\pi)\cos(x) + \sin(\pi)\sin(x) = -\cos(x)
(r_A + |DB|)^2 = |DB|^2 + |AB|^2 - 2|AB||DB|\cos(x)
(r_C + |DB|)^2 = |DB|^2 + |AB|^2 + 2|AB||DB|\cos(x)
